title: Star Trek New Voyages Mind Sifter Modern VFX in 5.1 Surround.mp4
description:
The newest release from Star Trek New Voyages/Phase 2.Captain Kirk is captured by Kor and subjected to the full power of the Klingons Mind Sifter device.Then Kirk is dumped into a 1950s era Insane Asylum.

This episode was written for the Star Trek Phase II in the 1970s,but not used when the revival of the series was aborted.Now it has been filmed and all I can say is enjoy!
